 +  where 3 = <built-in method count of list object at 0x70f666334b40>([53])
 +    where <built-in method count of list object at 0x70f666334b40> = [[53], [53, 1], [53], [53, 1], [53], []].count
 +  and   0 = <built-in method count of list object at 0x70f666334b40>([1, 53])
 +    where <built-in method count of list object at 0x70f666334b40> = [[53], [53, 1], [53], [53, 1], [53], []].count

 +  where 1 = <built-in function prod>([])
 +    where <built-in function prod> = math.prod
